# Google & Apple sign-in

Two halves: the **server side** (provider config stored in the moth
project — client IDs, Apple key) and the **app side** (native SDK setup
plus a small adapter class). The login screen shows a provider button as
soon as the provider is enabled in the project; until the app side is
done, tapping it explains what is missing instead of crashing.

